{"tid":242521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"婦搭𨋢遭夾腳拖行半層樓","createTime":"2017-05-14T03:38:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T15:29:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"742b8365b41208bf60ae6f4e266a1cc61ea97778","tid":242521,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:38:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20021056&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170514\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20021056%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170514&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=a387afe0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20021056%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170514&h=9759c7b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20021056&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170514</a><br />\n<br />\n婦搭𨋢遭夾腳拖行半層樓<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】葵涌葵星中心發生驚險升降機門夾腳意外，一名69歲婦人搭𨋢時，腳部被夾在升降機內門與𨋢槽牆壁之間，拖行了半層樓被困呼叫，驚動住客報警。消防員到場花一句鐘始將她救出。機電署初步調查懷疑是升降機不正常移動所致。<br />\n傷者姓蔡，雙腳骨折，現場為和宜合道1至3號葵星中心B座，樓齡36年，大堂有3部升降機，出事的為A𨋢。機電署稱，涉事升降機於1980年安裝，上一次定期檢驗日期為今年3月16日。有大廈住客指，涉事升降機於上月曾有故障。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n閉路電視拍攝到老婦雙腳被電梯門夾傷，倒在升降機內待救援情況。<br />\n<br />\n疑內門未關上出事<br />\n<br />\n昨下午3時許，蔡婦拉着買餸車從大廈19樓進入升降機時，疑升降機在內門仍未關上便啟動，事主雙腳被夾於𨋢門與樓層之間，並被拖至19樓與18樓之間始停下，她痛極呼叫，住在19樓姓司徒女住客稱：「當時聽到阿婆叫救命，好痛，快啲搵人救我。」通知保安報警。消防到場拯救一小時將她救出送院。機電署發言人稱，初步調查顯示相關事故涉及升降機不正常移動，並引致有乘客腳部被夾在升降機機廂門（內門）及樓層之間。署方已即時要求涉事升降機承辦商停止升降機運作以進行詳細檢驗，並提交事故報告。&nbsp;<br />\n■記者詹家志、溫文學"},{"pid":"c6c72082c7d05717133886d33644c30fc320d42d","tid":242521,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:39:53.000Z","msg":"閉路電視拍攝到老婦雙腳被電梯門夾傷，倒在升降機內待救援情況。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170514/large/a1102a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170514%2Flarge%2Fa1102a.gif&h=7ccb569e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88b8a96ddfc77c9ea088eddef1e35884c84dddb3","tid":242521,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:41:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>閉路電視拍攝到老婦雙腳被電梯門夾傷，倒在升降機內待救援情況。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170514/large/a1102a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170514%2Flarge%2Fa1102a.gif&h=7ccb569e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19221cf37ed90d815694c29baea967c81a861b21","tid":242521,"uid":80042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e425f719260a8943eb2200975e09e4ec9e31cd9b","tid":242521,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:53:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae3637c1c2aecfc25530ac1c775bddaeb29cfaab","tid":242521,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:54:21.000Z","msg":"口德<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd46fef647d4834a61af114e465ff97dec5aa67","tid":242521,"uid":60137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:55:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>閉路電視拍攝到老婦雙腳被電梯門夾傷，倒在升降機內待救援情況。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170514/large/a1102a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai